caption.text:
BONUS TIPS ⬇️

(don't forget to Like this post)

The "optimized" profile makes SUCH a difference!

Here are my ABC's of the perfect profile:
A - Attention grabbing profile picture

B - Bio begins with a "niche statement" that clearly & concisely tells us what your niche is

C - Concise! Use as few words as possible! K.I.S.S.

S - Searchable! The name plate (the bold text below your profile pic) is 100% searchable! I recommending putting a searchable title for your account on that line!

If you'd like me and my team to take a look at your profile and give you feedback, comment ME on this Reel!

caption.text:
Here’s why VIEWS are DOWN ⤵️ (and what to do)

First, let me say that views are down for almost EVERYONE!

According to a recent survey, 70% of people say that their views are down in the last few weeks! SO YOU AREN’T ALONE!

Here’s what’s going on:
1. There’s a lot going on in the world right now, distracting people from Instagram

2. People are spending less time consuming & more time creating

3. The algorithm is favoring SHARES above all else!

❌ Educational content is great, but doesn’t usually get shared.
❌ Tips & Tricks are great, but they don’t usually get shared.

🔑 Your focus should be on getting SHARES! 🔑

Here’s how:
1. “Needed this” content - motivational & inspirational posts.

2. “Call to arms” content - posts that are asking for help, especially for a good cause.

3. “That’s me” content - super relatable posts, like memes!

4. “Feather Ruffling” content - posts that are slightly controversial or unpopular opinions.

5. “In the know” content - like breaking news, pop culture, or trending moments

The final step is NOT ONLY creating shareworthy posts…
BUT THEN ASKING PEOPLE TO SHARE!

like this: ⤵️
If you can relate to feeling overwhelmed by Instagram, share this post to your Story!

caption.text:
I QUIT…

I’ve quit interviewing experts, and started sharing SUCCESS STORIES from REAL PEOPLE, just like you!! Comment STAN to listen!

No shade to any of my past guests or any of the experts I’ve had on the show,

But I often hear that experts (myself included) can be hard to relate to…

So that’s why I’m interviewing people like you, instead!

Moms, photographers, DJs, real estate agents, fitness instructors, etc… ALL TO ANSWER ONE QUESTION: ⤵️

HOW DO YOU GROW AND MAKE MONEY ON SOCIAL MEDIA?

I release new episodes every Monday, so comment STAN and I’ll send ya the link!

caption.text:
If you ever send people FROM Instagram TO other apps/sites, I HIGHLY recommend using Deep Links!! Comment the word “DEEP” to see how they work! ❤️

There are multiple sites that do this, but the one I use is called URL Genius (the website is: app.urlgeni.us) 👈

When using a deep link, the person who clicks the link is automatically logged in and thus, can comment, subscribe, like, follow, or do whatever it is you want them to do SO MUCH EASIER! 👏

If you learned something new, don’t forget to SAVE this post 🥰
